            <h2>Home</h2>
  					<p>Pampered and polished and ready to take on the world &ndash; that&rsquo;s exactly the way I want you to feel after our visit!</p>
<ol>
    <li>Simply put,&nbsp;I believe in high quality. High quality in services, products and experience.&nbsp;This is why I choose&nbsp;REDKEN products to bring out the ultimate beauty of&nbsp;your hair.&nbsp;Now add a&nbsp;customized design&nbsp;sculpted to accentuate your features coalesced with&nbsp;customized&nbsp;hair color and precise placement, and&nbsp;we have Hair Artistry.&nbsp;</li>
</ol>
<p>Whatever your preferred look, I&rsquo;m here to listen to your needs and carry out your wishes. Your preview of my <a href="http://niloohairdesign.com/services/">services</a> is just one click away. Then, for your added convenience, request an appointment with one more click to my <a href="http://niloohairdesign.com/contact-us/">contact form</a>.</p>
<p>Thank you for giving Niloo Hair Artistry (me) the opportunity to pamper you&hellip;and your hair!</p>
